node.text: Amazed by Zeina Nassar's strength and determination in taking action for her right, and the right of other women who wear headscarves, to box. Such a powerful example of how we can all #LeadWithLove. Watch more. #Tokyo2020 #PGPartner #StrongerTogether

shortcode_media.title: Good Is Gold: Zeina Nassar | P&G #LeadWithLove | Olympic Games Tokyo 2020
